comment: While it is still definitely horror, now I'm destroying a giant machine :D
Aaaaaaaaaaaaand done.  Boy did that get the heart pumping at the end

House burnt down at one of the properties at my post. Had to spend the last few hours coordinating with fire rescue and the HOA. Then spent the last hour playing whack a mole with news crews trying to get on scene with camera cranes and drones.
And now I can't freakin sleep when I've only gotten like 3 hours.
At this point your body is running on adrenaline
And by that I mean combination vacation / job search, ahahahaha
